'''不丹航空'''（{{lang-en|'''Bhutan Airlines'''}}，又称'''扎西航空'''（{{lang-en|'''Tashi Air Pvt. Ltd.'''}}），[[国际航空运输协会航空公司代码|IATA代码]]：'''B3'''；[[国际民航组织航空公司代码|ICAO代码]]：'''BTN'''，[[航空公司呼号|呼号]]：'''Bhutan Air'''）是[[不丹|不丹]]第一家非政府持有的航空公司。不丹航空2012年6月因为财务问题暂停了航班的运营，已于2013年10月恢复。<ref name=dca>{{cite web |url=http://www.dca.gov.bt/REGISTERED%20AIRLINES/Tashi%20Air |title=Tashi Air- Bhutan Airlines | Department of Civil Aviation - Bhutan |publisher=Dca.gov.bt |date= |accessdate=2012-01-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923213011/http://www.dca.gov.bt/REGISTERED%20AIRLINES/Tashi%20Air |archivedate=2015-09-23 }}</ref><ref name="intl">{{cite web |author=JL |url=http://airlineroute.net/2013/08/17/b3-ccubkk-oct13/ |title=Bhutan Airways to Start Kolkata / Bangkok Service from October 2013; Airline Route – Worldwide Airline Route Updates |publisher=Airlineroute.net |date=2013-08-17 |accessdate=2013-10-05 |archive-date=2013-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007020521/http://airlineroute.net/2013/08/17/b3-ccubkk-oct13/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="anna">{{cite web |url=http://www.anna.aero/2013/10/17/tashi-air-of-bhutan-starts-flights-to-bangkok/ |title=Tashi Air of Bhutan starts flights to Bangkok from Paro. |publisher=[[素万那普机场|素万那普机场]] |date=2013-10-17 |accessdate=2013-10-19 |archive-date=2017-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170820202751/http://www.anna.aero/2013/10/17/tashi-air-of-bhutan-starts-flights-to-bangkok/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=kuensel/>

== 历史 ==
不丹航空（当时称作扎西航空）于2011年12月4日成立。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tashigroup.bt/?page_id=862|title=Tashi Group - TASHI AIR LAUNCHED ON 4TH DEC. 2011|work=tashigroup.bt|accessdate=2014-12-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ChFysazs?url=http://www.tashigroup.bt/?page_id=862|archivedate=2012-12-06}}</ref>不丹航空为{{tsl|en|Tashi Group|扎西集团}}的子公司。不丹航空于2011年12月8日开始运营前往贾卡尔（{{lang|en|Jakar}}）和[[塔希冈|塔希冈]]的国内航线<ref name=tashigroup>{{cite web |url=http://www.tashigroup.bt/?page_id=862 |title=TASHI AIR LAUNCHED ON 4TH DEC. 2011 |publisher=Tashi Group |date=2011-12-04 |accessdate=2012-03-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6ChFysazs?url=http://www.tashigroup.bt/?page_id=862 |archivedate=2012-12-06 }}</ref>运营6个月后，航空公司向不丹政府申请开通更多国内航线。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bhutantraveldesigners.com/news/bhutan-airlines-wants-to-bow-out-for-a-while.html |title=Bhutan Airlines wants to bow out for a while. |publisher=Bhutan Travel Designers |date=2012-05-27 |accessdate=2013-10-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131011185647/http://www.bhutantraveldesigners.com/news/bhutan-airlines-wants-to-bow-out-for-a-while.html |archivedate=2013-10-11 }}</ref>公司靠向一立陶宛公司[[湿租|湿租]]的[[空中客车A319|空中客车A319]]运营所有航线。2013年7月30日，不丹航空接收其第二架空中客车A319。<ref name=anna/><ref name="kuensel">{{cite news|title=Tashi's Airbus A320 lands|first=Gyalsten|last=Dorji|url=http://www.kuenselonline.com/tashis-airbus-a320-lands/#.UlA_5hBvCdk|newspaper={{tsl|en|Kuensel||Kuensel Online}}|date=2013-10-03|accessdate=2013-10-05|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005233859/http://www.kuenselonline.com/tashis-airbus-a320-lands/#.UlA_5hBvCdk|archivedate=2013-10-05}}</ref><ref name="bhutanairlines.bt">{{cite web|url=http://www.bhutanairlines.bt/#hometabs-1|title=Bhutan Airlines - Fly with us to the Land of Happiness|work=bhutanairlines.bt|accessdate=2014-12-12|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201084912/http://www.bhutanairlines.bt/#hometabs-1|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 办公室 ==
不丹航空总部位于[[廷布|廷布]]的扎西商场。公司在帕罗机场也有办公室。<ref name=omgexp>{{cite web |url=http://omgexp.com/en/about/omgexp |title=OMG Experience (Bhutan Airlines GSA) |publisher=OMG Experience |date=2013-12-04 |accessdate=2013-03-30 |archive-date=2020-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102084734/http://omgexp.com/en/about/omgexp |dead-url=no }}</ref>其他辦公室位於加德滿都、尼泊爾和馬來西亞。<ref name=bhutanairlines>{{cite web |url=http://www.bhutanairlines.bt/ouroffice |title=Bhutan Airlines - Our Offices |publisher=Tashi Group |date=2011-12-04 |accessdate=2012-03-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324172429/http://www.bhutanairlines.bt/ouroffice |archivedate=2014-03-24 }}</ref>

